creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Komische Lyrik von Busch und Morgenstern by Various.
Read in German by bettine
Dies ist eine Auswahl von deutschen Gedichten komischer Lyrik von Wilhelm Busch und Christian Morgenstern.
This is a selection of German comical and nonsense poems. (Zusammenfassung von bettine)
For further information, including links to M4B audio book, online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
